# Crypto Tracker Website

## Description
A live crypto price tracker that fetches data from the CoinGecko API and displays it with a modern UI.

## Features
- Light/Dark mode toggle (based on user's preference, can be switched using toggle-theme
-Generates a graph to display changes of Crypto Coin
- Live prices auto-refresh every 2 minute
- Search bar to filter coins
- Responsive design


## How to Run
1. Open `index.html` in your browser.
2. Ensure you have an internet connection for the API.

## Tech Stack
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- CoinGecko API
